channel.title: Running private serves on mac?
channel.description:
i have bee able to run 317's on mac's without having to use a .jar or another mac compatible file. by using commands in terminal i found online. but does anyone know how to run a 525 one?
to run a 317 on a mac all you would do is type in terminal "cd (file name here) press enter than copy and paste this "/System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/1.6.0/Home/bin/java -Xmx500m client 66 live live software members english game0"
and it would run. but it does not work with 508+ any help appreciated, thank you!
